## Development

### Setup

```bash
pip install -e ".[dev]"
pre-commit install
```

### Testing

```bash
# Run all tests
pytest

# With coverage
pytest --cov=smarteda --cov-report=html

# Specific test file
pytest tests/test_data_loader.py -v
```

### Code Quality

```bash
# Formatting
black src/ tests/

# Linting
ruff check src/ tests/

# Type checking
mypy src/smarteda
```

